        // read from: aWindLaneA, aWindLaneB, aScrapLaneA, aWindLaneC, aWindLaneD, aScrapLaneB, aWaterLaneC, aWaterLaneD, aSnowLaneA, aSnowLaneB, aSnowLaneC
